	&lt;li&gt;Adds HExecutionEngine abstract class to o.a.p.backend.hadoop.executionengine.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Moves MRExecutionEngine from o.a.p.backend.hadoop.executionengine to o.a.p.backend.hadoop.executionengine.mapReduceLayer.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Converts some utility functions to public static functions in Utils.java.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
